541
00:31:56,299 --> 00:31:58,779
[SPEAKER_00] Isuse, šta je ovo?

542
00:31:58,779 --> 00:32:00,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ovi nisu normalni.

543
00:32:00,079 --> 00:32:00,680
[SPEAKER_00] Šta ovo?

544
00:32:00,680 --> 00:32:01,720
[SPEAKER_00] Niti ovo hrvatski,

545
00:32:01,720 --> 00:32:02,579
