546
00:32:02,579 --> 00:32:03,460
[SPEAKER_00] Šta ovi pričaju?

547
00:32:03,460 --> 00:32:05,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ne idem ti ja više.

548
00:32:05,819 --> 00:32:07,059
[SPEAKER_00] Nema šanse.

549
00:32:07,059 --> 00:32:08,140
[SPEAKER_00] Ma i ti dioćeš,

550
00:32:08,140 --> 00:32:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] ovi nisu normalni.

551
00:32:09,000 --> 00:32:09,940
[SPEAKER_00] Nema mene vuč tamo.

552
00:32:09,940 --> 00:32:11,839
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se bunim,

553
00:32:11,839 --> 00:32:12,240
[SPEAKER_00] gunđam,

554
00:32:12,240 --> 00:32:13,099
[SPEAKER_00] ja prigovaram,

555
00:32:13,099 --> 00:32:14,839
[SPEAKER_00] a mama šuti, moli.

556
00:32:14,839 --> 00:32:15,900
[SPEAKER_00] Mudra žena.

557
00:32:15,900 --> 00:32:17,339
[SPEAKER_00] Šuti, moli.

558
00:32:17,339 --> 00:32:19,480
[SPEAKER_00] I opet prođe možda po godine.

559
00:32:19,559 --> 00:32:20,640
[SPEAKER_00] Aj, dođi, aj, bit će,

560
00:32:20,640 --> 00:32:21,900
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam ovo, bit će ono.

561
00:32:21,900 --> 00:32:23,200
[SPEAKER_00] I dođem ja na seminar

562
00:32:23,200 --> 00:32:24,240
[SPEAKER_00] Patera Zvijezdana,

563
00:32:24,240 --> 00:32:25,640
[SPEAKER_00] Sveti Franjo,

564
00:32:25,640 --> 00:32:26,460
