565
00:32:26,460 --> 00:32:27,680
[SPEAKER_00] ovako, početkom desetoga,

566
00:32:27,680 --> 00:32:28,720
[SPEAKER_00] oni imaju te seminare.

567
00:32:28,720 --> 00:32:30,400
[SPEAKER_00] Pa to mi se svidilo.

568
00:32:30,400 --> 00:32:32,079
[SPEAKER_00] To baš ono bilo lijepo.

569
00:32:32,079 --> 00:32:33,359
[SPEAKER_00] Aj, sljedeći seminar

570
00:32:33,359 --> 00:32:34,299
