572
00:32:36,019 --> 00:32:37,640
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je, ovo je, ovo je pak super.

573
00:32:37,640 --> 00:32:39,200
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je sad super.

574
00:32:39,200 --> 00:32:40,759
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je čovjek priča

575
00:32:40,759 --> 00:32:43,859
