577
00:32:45,319 --> 00:32:47,519
[SPEAKER_00] Kako nas neprijatelj kuša.

578
00:32:47,519 --> 00:32:50,099
[SPEAKER_00] Kako se on ponaša perfidno

579
00:32:50,099 --> 00:32:51,579
