[SPEAKER_00] a maltretira nas.

582
00:32:54,160 --> 00:32:57,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ho, ovo je jako dobro.

583
00:32:57,119 --> 00:32:59,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ovdje ja mogu nešto naučiti.

584
00:32:59,900 --> 00:33:01,539
[SPEAKER_00] I udicu je Bog bacio.

585
00:33:01,539 --> 00:33:03,200
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam se uhvatila

586
00:33:03,200 --> 00:33:04,559
[SPEAKER_00] za Božju udicu.

587
00:33:04,559 --> 00:33:06,660
[SPEAKER_00] Kad mi je to počelo biti zanimljivo,

588
00:33:06,660 --> 00:33:07,559
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam počela dolaziti

589
00:33:07,559 --> 00:33:08,359
[SPEAKER_00] na svaki susret.

590
00:33:08,359 --> 00:33:09,160
