591
00:33:09,160 --> 00:33:11,220
[SPEAKER_00] na Selskoj u Marka Križevčanja.

592
00:33:11,220 --> 00:33:13,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam počela išti jedno

593
00:33:13,460 --> 00:33:15,660
[SPEAKER_00] i onda sam počela kupovat literaturu.

594
00:33:15,660 --> 00:33:16,700
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo mi je premalo.

595
00:33:16,700 --> 00:33:19,619
[SPEAKER_00] Počela sam kupovat sve što se dalo naći o vjeri.

596
00:33:19,619 --> 00:33:21,619
[SPEAKER_00] O molitvi, o vjeri,

597
00:33:21,619 --> 00:33:24,079
[SPEAKER_00] o istinama vjere.

598
00:33:24,079 --> 00:33:26,259
[SPEAKER_00] Ma, kupovala sam sve život.

599
00:33:26,259 --> 00:33:27,519
[SPEAKER_00] Tako sam kupila dokumente

600
00:33:27,519 --> 00:33:29,180
[SPEAKER_00] drugog Vatikanskog koncila.

601
00:33:29,359 --> 00:33:31,299
[SPEAKER_00] Sve živo sam kupao.

602
00:33:31,299 --> 00:33:33,559
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, gutala sam knjige,

603
00:33:33,559 --> 00:33:35,119
[SPEAKER_00] hodala sam u tramaju,

604
00:33:35,119 --> 00:33:36,799
[SPEAKER_00] ovak, ne vidim.

605
00:33:36,799 --> 00:33:38,420
[SPEAKER_00] Non stop sam čitala knjige.

606
00:33:38,420 --> 00:33:39,519
[SPEAKER_00] Zaspim sa knjigom,

607
00:33:39,519 --> 00:33:40,920
[SPEAKER_00] probudim se, uhvatim

608
00:33:40,920 --> 00:33:42,160
[SPEAKER_00] i čitam dalje.

609
00:33:42,160 --> 00:33:44,079
[SPEAKER_00] Na stotine knjiga sam pročitala.

610
00:33:44,079 --> 00:33:44,920
[SPEAKER_00] Na stotine.

611
00:33:44,920 --> 00:33:48,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ali što, bila mi je duša gladna.

612
00:33:48,279 --> 00:33:50,880
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon toga je Bog providio

613
00:33:50,880 --> 00:33:52,519
[SPEAKER_00] opet sljedeća stvar,

614
00:33:52,519 --> 00:33:53,619
[SPEAKER_00] Međugorje.

615
00:33:53,619 --> 00:33:55,380
[SPEAKER_00] Gospa se ukaza,

616
00:33:55,380 --> 00:33:57,319
[SPEAKER_00] a moji se još iskopije iši u Međugorje.

617
00:33:57,319 --> 00:33:58,559
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je vojska zatvarala,

618
00:33:58,680 --> 00:33:59,539
[SPEAKER_00] kad se nije smijelo,

619
00:33:59,539 --> 00:34:01,140
[SPEAKER_00] oni su se provukli

620
00:34:01,140 --> 00:34:02,859
[SPEAKER_00] i iskopija ranu u Međugorje.

621
00:34:02,859 --> 00:34:04,660
[SPEAKER_00] I sad od svih tih priča,

622
00:34:04,660 --> 00:34:06,059
[SPEAKER_00] ja hoću ići u Međugorje.

623
00:34:06,059 --> 00:34:07,859
[SPEAKER_00] Sad, šta da očekujem,

624
00:34:07,859 --> 00:34:08,519
[SPEAKER_00] majko Mila?

625
00:34:08,519 --> 00:34:10,260
[SPEAKER_00] Onda u busu svjedoče ljudi

626
00:34:10,260 --> 00:34:10,940
[SPEAKER_00] koji su već bili.

627
00:34:11,260 --> 00:34:12,260
[SPEAKER_00] Gospa se ukazuje,

628
00:34:12,260 --> 00:34:13,219
[SPEAKER_00] sunce se vrti,

629
00:34:13,219 --> 00:34:14,139
[SPEAKER_00] ovo se ovako.

630
00:34:14,139 --> 00:34:15,199
[SPEAKER_00] Isu se, Bože,

631
00:34:15,199 --> 00:34:16,340
[SPEAKER_00] šta da ja sad očekujem,

632
00:34:16,340 --> 00:34:16,960
[SPEAKER_00] šta će to biti?

633
00:34:16,960 --> 00:34:17,719
[SPEAKER_00] Bože,

634
00:34:17,719 --> 00:34:18,980
[SPEAKER_00] oprosti,

635
00:34:18,980 --> 00:34:19,940
[SPEAKER_00] ali mene ovo,

636
00:34:19,940 --> 00:34:21,619
[SPEAKER_00] ja ne znam šta da očekujem.

637
00:34:21,619 --> 00:34:22,760
[SPEAKER_00] Evo mene,

638
00:34:22,760 --> 00:34:24,760
[SPEAKER_00] pa ti sad šta goćeš napravi.

639
00:34:24,760 --> 00:34:25,539
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

640
00:34:25,539 --> 00:34:26,539
