642
00:34:27,219 --> 00:34:27,739
[SPEAKER_00] Evo mene,

643
00:34:27,739 --> 00:34:29,460
[SPEAKER_00] ja nemam pojma šta je ovo sad sve.

644
00:34:29,460 --> 00:34:30,300
[SPEAKER_00] Evo me.

645
00:34:31,300 --> 00:34:33,360
[SPEAKER_00] I u Međugorju me baš pola,

646
00:34:33,360 --> 00:34:34,460
[SPEAKER_00] ono doslovce,

647
00:34:34,460 --> 00:34:35,320
[SPEAKER_00] sastavilo.

648
00:34:35,320 --> 00:34:36,800
[SPEAKER_00] Sastavilo.

649
00:34:36,800 --> 00:34:39,420
[SPEAKER_00] Milost Božja me sastavila po Mariji.

650
00:34:39,420 --> 00:34:40,800
[SPEAKER_00] Baš ono,

651
00:34:40,800 --> 00:34:42,519
