654
00:34:46,719 --> 00:34:48,139
[SPEAKER_00] tad sam imala 19 godina,

655
00:34:48,139 --> 00:34:50,400
[SPEAKER_00] da sam ja mogla reći Bogu svoj da.

656
00:34:50,400 --> 00:34:51,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ne da se bunim.

657
00:34:51,820 --> 00:34:52,599
[SPEAKER_00] Inače,

658
00:34:52,599 --> 00:34:53,880
[SPEAKER_00] moj iskustvo prvo,

659
00:34:53,880 --> 00:34:55,039
[SPEAKER_00] iskustvo molitve,

660
00:34:55,039 --> 00:34:56,119
[SPEAKER_00] doma,

661
00:34:56,119 --> 00:34:57,760
[SPEAKER_00] znači nas je jako puno,

662
00:34:57,760 --> 00:34:59,260
[SPEAKER_00] i moli se krunica.

663
00:34:59,260 --> 00:35:00,800
[SPEAKER_00] Sad si možete misliti,

664
00:35:01,000 --> 00:35:01,460
[SPEAKER_00] dijete,

665
00:35:01,460 --> 00:35:02,940
[SPEAKER_00] i zdravo Mario,

666
00:35:02,940 --> 00:35:03,900
[SPEAKER_00] i sveta Mario,

667
00:35:03,900 --> 00:35:04,599
[SPEAKER_00] 50 puta.

668
00:35:04,599 --> 00:35:05,719
[SPEAKER_00] Hajde.

669
00:35:05,719 --> 00:35:06,719
[SPEAKER_00] Ja si mislim,

670
00:35:06,719 --> 00:35:09,219
