671
00:35:09,219 --> 00:35:10,820
[SPEAKER_00] pa dosta više,

672
00:35:10,820 --> 00:35:11,659
[SPEAKER_00] to zdravo Mario,

673
00:35:11,659 --> 00:35:12,280
[SPEAKER_00] sveta Mario,

674
00:35:12,280 --> 00:35:13,760
