686
00:35:28,219 --> 00:35:28,820
[SPEAKER_00] tak je red.

687
00:35:28,820 --> 00:35:30,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam jedva čekala da odvrte,

688
00:35:30,860 --> 00:35:32,079
