689
00:35:32,079 --> 00:35:33,179
[SPEAKER_00] briga me za krunicu.

690
00:35:33,179 --> 00:35:34,739
[SPEAKER_00] Uglavnom,

691
00:35:34,739 --> 00:35:36,699
