692
00:35:36,699 --> 00:35:38,880
[SPEAKER_00] sad dođem u Međugorje

693
00:35:38,880 --> 00:35:40,679
[SPEAKER_00] i slušam gospine poruke.

694
00:35:40,679 --> 00:35:41,679
[SPEAKER_00] Post,

695
00:35:41,679 --> 00:35:43,139
[SPEAKER_00] molitva,

696
00:35:43,139 --> 00:35:44,619
[SPEAKER_00] ispovjed,

697
00:35:45,099 --> 00:35:45,820
[SPEAKER_00] klanjanje,

698
00:35:45,820 --> 00:35:49,019
[SPEAKER_00] pa di sam ja do sad bila u vjeri,

699
00:35:49,019 --> 00:35:50,519
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam mislila da nešto znam.

700
00:35:50,519 --> 00:35:53,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo sad drugi vitam uvest.

701
00:35:53,460 --> 00:35:55,179
[SPEAKER_00] Molitva krunice,

702
00:35:55,179 --> 00:35:57,539
[SPEAKER_00] ali ta krunica koja je mišna na živce,

703
00:35:57,539 --> 00:35:58,659
