704
00:35:58,659 --> 00:36:00,260
[SPEAKER_00] Po tim dosadnim,

705
00:36:00,260 --> 00:36:01,340
[SPEAKER_00] vjernim činima,

706
00:36:01,340 --> 00:36:02,599
[SPEAKER_00] gledajte,

707
00:36:02,599 --> 00:36:03,619
[SPEAKER_00] dosadnim na prvu,

708
00:36:03,619 --> 00:36:04,639
[SPEAKER_00] vjernim činima,

709
00:36:04,639 --> 00:36:07,500
[SPEAKER_00] je Bog gledao stav moga srca.

710
00:36:08,619 --> 00:36:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Stav iznutra.

711
00:36:10,000 --> 00:36:12,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ću biti vjerna

712
00:36:12,099 --> 00:36:14,059
