714
00:36:15,420 --> 00:36:17,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ću se truditi tako.

715
00:36:17,340 --> 00:36:19,159
[SPEAKER_00] I onda sam išla,

716
00:36:19,159 --> 00:36:20,460
