719
00:36:23,400 --> 00:36:26,599
[SPEAKER_00] To mi je bilo jako, jako ljekovito za srce.

720
00:36:26,599 --> 00:36:28,679
[SPEAKER_00] Tada sam prvi puta u Međugorje,

721
00:36:28,679 --> 00:36:29,159
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam bila,

722
00:36:29,159 --> 00:36:30,360
[SPEAKER_00] sam predala život Bogu.

723
00:36:30,360 --> 00:36:32,260
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam ni znala da je to novo rođenje,

724
00:36:32,260 --> 00:36:33,619
