725
00:36:33,619 --> 00:36:36,719
[SPEAKER_00] ali sam prvi puta svjesno rekla Bogu da.

726
00:36:37,719 --> 00:36:38,900
[SPEAKER_00] I od onda,

727
00:36:38,900 --> 00:36:39,460
