731
00:36:45,019 --> 00:36:47,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam dolazila u situacije,

732
00:36:47,380 --> 00:36:49,079
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi otac Ralf Diorio,

733
00:36:49,079 --> 00:36:50,559
[SPEAKER_00] opet, prvi susred,

734
00:36:50,559 --> 00:36:53,480
