735
00:36:53,480 --> 00:36:55,099
[SPEAKER_00] svećani karizmatske obnove,

736
00:36:55,099 --> 00:36:56,340
[SPEAKER_00] on u Međugorju.

737
00:36:56,340 --> 00:36:58,440
[SPEAKER_00] Mi vozimo cijelu noš da tam dođemo,

738
00:36:58,440 --> 00:36:59,960
[SPEAKER_00] tražim ga po Međugorju,

